data.description: Location, location, location! Look no further, prime Westport real estate! This 3.25 acre piece of property is located directly off Highway-105 on the way to Westport and includes over 400 ft. of highway frontage. The property includes a 1388 sq. ft. 3 bed 1 bath w/ connected shed, 1064 sq. ft. attached carport and additional 320 sq. ft. covered space for RV parking. This property is currently zoned residential but with the right permitting could be used in a variety of different ways.
